<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="welcome">
        Welcome <%= @visitor.current_user.username %>!
        <div class="visitors">
          <%= @visitor.count_of_visitors %> unique visitors.<br>
          <a href="https://github.com/login/oauth/authorize?client_id=<%= ENV["CLIENT_ID"] %>&scope=repo">Login with GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="title box-1">
        <div class="notice">
          Hover over me!
        </div>
        <div class="glitch-animation" title="Under Construction">
          Under Construction
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          First and foremost - I'm a junior backend engineer, with few presentable projects of my own to speak for. I can (and have) spent hours fiddling with CSS for lackluster results. So, instead, I opted for functionality on this portfolio site. Such as, identifying unique users, GitHub oauth, and eventually I'll incorporate comments and <a href="https://beta.openai.com/docs/introduction/key-concepts" target="_blank">OpenAI.</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
